text: I'm a network technician at Amazon Web
Services here at AWS is always room to
learn and grow in every direction after
nine years in the United States Coast
Guard and a couple more as an accountant
I joined AWS to the military
apprenticeship program in search of a
greater challenge it was easily the best
decision I've ever made it's a constant
learning process for me and my new job
it's a completely different industry
where I have to familiarize myself with
new technology every day put extra hours
to fulfill the needs and demands of our
very diverse and extensive projects all
while finding time to look out for
trends in this ever-changing industry I
firmly believe that AWS cares about me
and my career growth my name is David
Cologne and I am the Builder
